headline.print_headline: Ex-Carter's Executives, NY Fund Manager Get Prison for Insider Trading
headline.main: Ex-Carter's Executives, NY Fund Manager Get Prison for Insider Trading

lead_paragraph: Two former executives at Carter's Inc and a New York hedge fund manager received prison sentences on Tuesday for engaging in an insider trading conspiracy involving the children's clothing company's stock.
